The game is supposed to improve your Sense of Bar™ by giving you an opportunity to click once a period. The game consists of three parts:
 in the first part you assign a duration in beats per minutes(the default interval is 120 bpm (half a second)); 
 in the second part the game starts (click on the screen once per period), and ends by pressing the big red button; 
 in the third part your results summarize. And remember: the longer you play, the more accurate your result.

The game is supposed to improve your speed reaction by giving you an opportunity to click on screen. The game consists of three parts:
 in the first part you assign amount of tries (the default value is 1); 
 in the second part the game starts (click on the screen when it is red); 
 in the third part your results summarize.

This famous game is supposed to improve your speed reaction and bullseye. The game consists of three parts:
 in the first part you assign duration in seconds (the default value is 10 seconds); 
 in the second part the game starts (whack a mole); 
 in the third part your hits summarize.
